<mxfile host="app.diagrams.net" agent="Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/138.0.0.0 YaBrowser/25.8.0.0 Safari/537.36" version="29.0.3"> <diagram name="Страница-1" id="CQvb66rGIvkdJHibp9St"> <mxGraphModel dx="3218" dy="2420" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="827" pageHeight="1169" math="0" shadow="0"> <root> <mxCell id="0" /> <mxCell id="1" parent="0" /> <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{
 "data": "@startuml Learning_Session_Sequence
actor \"Пользователь\" as User
participant \"Интерфейс\" as UI
participant \"LearningController\" as Controller
participant \"LearningService\" as LearningService
participant \"SpacedRepetition\" as SRS
participant \"База данных\" as DB

User -> UI: Нажимает \"Учить\" на колоде
activate User
activate UI

UI -> Controller: GET /api/decks/1/learning-session
activate Controller

Controller -> LearningService: startLearningSession(1)
activate LearningService

LearningService -> DB: SELECT * FROM Cards \nWHERE deck_id = 1 \nAND (next_review_date <= NOW() OR next_review_date IS NULL)
activate DB
DB -> LearningService: cards_for_review
deactivate DB

LearningService -> LearningService: shuffleCards(cards_for_review)
activate LearningService

LearningService -> Controller: LearningSessionResponse(cards_for_review)
deactivate LearningService

Controller -> UI: 200 OK\n{cards: [...], session_id: 123}
deactivate Controller

UI -> UI: Показать первую карточку (вопрос)
UI -> User: \"Hello\" (вопрос)

== Цикл обучения ==
loop Для каждой карточки
 User -> UI: Кликает на карточку
 UI -> UI: Переворачивает карточку
 UI -> User: \"Привет\" (ответ)
 
 User -> UI: Выбирает оценку \"Хорошо\"
 UI -> Controller: POST /api/reviews\n{card_id: 1, rating: \"good\", session_id: 123}
 activate Controller
 
 Controller -> LearningService: rateCard(1, \"good\", 123)
 activate LearningService
 
 LearningService -> SRS: calculateNextReview(1, \"good\")
 activate SRS
 SRS -> SRS: applySM2Algorithm(ease_factor, interval)
 activate SRS
 SRS -> LearningService: {next_review_date: \"2024-12-05\", interval_days: 3}
 deactivate SRS
 
 LearningService -> DB: INSERT INTO CardReviews\n(card_id, rating, next_review_date, interval_days)
 activate DB
 DB -> LearningService: review_id
 deactivate DB
 
 LearningService -> DB: UPDATE Cards SET next_review_date = \"2024-12-05\"\nWHERE card_id = 1
 activate DB
 DB -> LearningService: updated
 deactivate DB
 
 LearningService -> Controller: SuccessResponse()
 deactivate LearningService
 
 Controller -> UI: 200 OK
 deactivate Controller
 
 UI -> UI: Показать следующую карточку
 UI -> User: Новый вопрос
end

UI -> UI: Показать \"Обучение завершено!\"
UI -> User: Статистика сессии
deactivate UI
deactivate User
@enduml",
